<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>myTamilDate Email Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7e9ff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 700px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 1.5rem;
        }

        .logo-container {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            display: block;
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #e53e3e;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .text {
            color: #4a4a4a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .link {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .button {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            background-color: #f97316;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #ea580c;
        }

        .tips-link {
            color: #a855f7;
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .image-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .social-icons a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #6b7280;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .social-icons a:hover {
            color: #374151;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="<%= logo %>" alt="myTamilDate Logo" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="title">You've successfully signed up for myTamilDate.com!</h1>
        <p class="text">
            We're thrilled to have you as a member of the myTamilDate community! Ready to meet some amazing single
            Tamils from
            around the world?
        </p>
        <div style="margin-left: auto; width: fit-content;">
            <a href="https://mytamildate.waysdatalabs.com/Signinoptions" class="button">Start Matching!</a>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="tips-link">Here are some tips to help you make the most of your membership</a>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="./images/mobile.png" alt="App Preview"
                style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 10px;" />
        </div>
        <div style="margin-inline: auto; width: fit-content;">
            <a href="#" class="button" style="background-color: #a855f7;">Watch the video</a>
        </div>
    </div>
